      <div id="center" >
                              								<h1>Office of International Students and Scholars</h1>
										<div id="node-795" class="node">

  
  <div class="content">
 	    <h3>Office Hours</h3>
<p>Monday - Friday<br />
	9:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
<h3>Walk-in Advising Hours</h3>
<p>Monday - Friday<br />
	1:00 p.m. - 4:00 p.m.</p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6em;">NYU-Poly is home to over 2300 graduate and undergraduate international students and scholars from 60 countries. Our office is here to help you make a successful transition to our community. We will make every effort to offer you a warm and nourishing environment and help you address some of the challenges you might encounter during your academic program at NYU-Poly. We encourage you to visit our office, ask questions, and seek guidance and advice.</span></p>
<p>Please note that OISS has moved recently. We are now located in the Dibner Building, LC230.</p>
  </div>

